name: Spinnaker 0.29.0
body:
Various config and docs tweaks.

Installing spinnaker suppresses auto upstart boot of its microservices.
Spinnaker itself will explicitly auto start them when it starts.
There should be no visible behavior change from this unless you had previously modified the standard microservice configurations to upstart on boot rather than wait to be started by the spinnaker service.
